data.description: **Highly motivated sellers offering a $5,000 seller concession to be used at buyers discretion with acceptable offer**Come see this exquisite home located in the Curtis Pond neighborhood! This property boasts the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic style. This home features an open and airy floor plan. Enjoy the convenience of a bedroom on the main level, which could also be converted to an office! Beautiful kitchen that is open to the living and dining areas makes it perfect for gatherings and entertaining. Upstairs you will be greeted by a large loft area and four bedrooms! The primary suite features an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. Enjoy the privacy of a fenced in backyard! Don't miss the opportunity to make this gorgeous residence your new home! Come and embrace the charm and comfort that this Mooresville gem as to offer!
